title: Bavette Steak & Blistered Shishito Peppers with Charred Corn Feta Salad, Fresh Tomato Salsa & Rice
description: This Mexican-inspired meal stars juicy seared bavette steaks served alongside charred corn and feta salad tossed with cilantro and lime and a little chili powder for just enough kick. Blistered sweet (and sometimes spicy!) shishito peppers accompany the steak, along with fluffy rice topped with fresh tomato salsa.
